0:00:00.000,0:00:03.240
Paunobva pano unoenda kupi, Madhamu?

0:00:03.240,0:00:04.900
Yola.

0:00:04.900,0:00:07.600
Kunaani?

0:00:07.600,0:00:09.420
Ndinogara namai vangu.

0:00:09.420,0:00:13.480
Nokuti ndiri kuona uchigara woga.

0:00:13.480,0:00:16.380
Dambudziko rako nderei?

0:00:16.380,0:00:17.880
Iwe urikushunguridzika.

0:00:17.880,0:00:19.140
Hongu changamire.

0:00:19.140,0:00:23.600
Uye kushungurudzika uku kwakaita kuti iwe uite zvinhu zvakawanda zvausingadi kuita.

0:00:23.600,0:00:24.660
Hongu changamire.

0:00:24.660,0:00:26.280
Uye iwe waneta zvino.

0:00:26.280,0:00:28.500
Hongu changamire.

0:00:28.500,0:00:33.640
Paiva nemurume waive naye kwenguva yakati asi wakazomusiya.

0:00:33.640,0:00:35.040
Hongu changamire. - Chii chakaitika?

0:00:35.040,0:00:39.200
Pane chimwe chinhu chawakawana.

0:00:39.200,0:00:40.000
Uyu mwanasikana wako.

0:00:40.000,0:00:41.160
Hongu changamire.

0:00:41.160,0:00:43.980
Ini ndirikuti mwanasikana wenyu mwanasikana arikutambudzika.

0:00:43.980,0:00:45.540
Hongu changamire.

0:00:45.540,0:00:49.240
Ndine zvinetso. Takauya kubva kure kose uko ku Yola.

0:00:49.240,0:00:50.540
Tabva ku Yola.

0:00:50.540,0:00:52.000
Iwe hauzive zviri kuitika.

0:00:52.000,0:00:55.140
Hungu, changamire, handizivi kunyange muupenyu hwangu.

0:00:55.140,0:00:56.860
Handeyi.

0:00:56.860,0:01:02.800
NHUNGAMIRO YE HUPENYU

0:01:02.800,0:01:06.340
Zita rangu ndi Doris. Ini ndiri weku Yola.

0:01:06.340,0:01:12.460
Svondo ye vhiki rapera, Munhu wa Mwari akauya pandiri uye akaporofita.

0:01:12.460,0:01:16.260
Akandibvunza kuti ndaizoenda kupi ndichibva pano.

0:01:16.260,0:01:21.440
Akandiona ndichigara ndega uye kuti ndakanga ndakagumbuka uye ndakaneta.

0:01:21.440,0:01:25.640
Izvozvo zvakaita kuti ndiite zvinhu zvandisingadi kuita.

0:01:25.640,0:01:29.900
Akati ndakasiyana nemurume nokuti ndakawana chimwe chinhu

0:01:29.900,0:01:36.000
uye kuti ndakanga ndiri mwanasikana anetseka izvo zviri zvechokwadi .

0:01:36.000,0:01:43.640
Paakandibvunza kuti ndaizoendepi ndichibva pano, ndakati Yola asi ku Yola zvinhu zvakanga zvakaoma kwatiri.

0:01:43.640,0:01:49.320
Rendi yepatiri kugara yapera uye hatina mari yekubhadhara imba yatiri kurenda.

0:01:49.320,0:01:55.620
Vanhu vanondiona sokunge ndiri pakanaka uye sokunge ndine mari asi hapana chandinacho.

0:01:55.620,0:01:58.720
Izvi zvakonzera kushungurudzika.

0:01:58.720,0:02:05.320
Ndakatoedza kuzvibaya kakawanda kuti ndizviuraye asi amai vangu vaizouya vachindibata.

0:02:05.320,0:02:12.080
Ndaneta nehupenyu hwandiri kurarama.

0:02:12.080,0:02:15.820
Handina mushando, hapana chandinacho.

0:02:15.820,0:02:23.740
Tarisa kwandiri; Ndinofanira kunge ndakaroorwa asi hapana murume ari kuuya.

0:02:23.740,0:02:28.480
Saka, zvakataurwa nemunhu wa Mwari pamusoro pezvako zvakange zviri zvechokwadi paakabvunza kuti uri kuenda kupi -

0:02:28.480,0:02:30.700
chaizvoizvo hauna kwekuenda ikozvino.

0:02:30.700,0:02:31.840
Hongu.

0:02:31.840,0:02:35.160
Zvakanaka Tinganzwe izwi kana maviri kubva kuna amai vako here?

0:02:35.160,0:02:41.840
Ndinovimba kuti ivowo vane chimwe chinhu chekutaura

0:02:41.840,0:02:43.960
Emanueri! (Mwari nesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:02:43.960,0:02:45.820
Isu tinobva ku Yola.

0:02:45.820,0:02:53.620
Apo patakasvika pano, munhu wa Mwari akaprofita kumwanasikana wangu kuti akanga ari mwanasikana anotambudzika.

0:02:53.620,0:02:59.540
Zvadaro, ndakasimuka ndikati hongu kunyange ini pachangu.

0:02:59.540,0:03:02.440
Gare gare, munhu wa Mwari akati tinofanira kuuya kuzomuona.

0:03:02.440,0:03:04.380
Saka, hupenyu hwedu hunosuruvarisa.

0:03:04.380,0:03:06.340
Kunyange apo akabvunza kuti taizoenda kupi ...

0:03:06.340,0:03:08.780
Hatina kokuenda. Hatina nzvimbo yekuenda.

0:03:08.780,0:03:12.780
Hatina kokuenda nokuti iye zvino, hatina chinhu.

0:03:12.780,0:03:16.660
Anoda kuzviuraya; iye anoda kuzvibaya.

0:03:16.660,0:03:19.840
Chero nguva ipi zvayo yaanotora banga kuti azviuraye pachake, ndaizomubata.

0:03:19.840,0:03:23.220
Ndaizotaura naye ndichiti anofanira kuvimba na Mwari nokuti

0:03:23.220,0:03:26.940
Mwari ndiye Mwari anoita kuti zvisingakwanisike zviitike.

0:03:26.940,0:03:32.880
Tisati tauya pano, ndaifunga kuti zvingaitike sei kuti isu tiuye pano nokuti pakanga pasina nzira.

0:03:32.880,0:03:35.100
Mumwe munhu akandipa zvimwe zvinhu zvokutengesa.

0:03:35.100,0:03:40.780
Ini ndakabva ndamutora ndokuti, huya, ngatimhanyire kuna baba vedu, T.B. Joshua

0:03:40.780,0:03:44.420
Ndinofunga kuti ino ndiyo nzvimbo yekupedzisira

0:03:44.420,0:03:46.380
Saka, madhamu, tinongoda kunzwa kubva kwamuri.

0:03:46.380,0:03:50.480
Iwe muri kuona mudzimai wechikuru achichema misodzi nekuda kwemamiriro ezvinhu avange vari maari, kwemakore.

0:03:50.480,0:03:56.060
Imi mati munhu wa Mwari akanga aporofita kuti mwanasikana wenyu aiva mwana arikutambudzika.

0:03:56.060,0:04:01.720
Mungatiudze here zvakawanda pamusoro pezvinetso izvo mwana wenyu ange akatarisana nazvo, musati mapihwa uporofita,

0:04:01.720,0:04:04.380
panguva yesvondo yekupedzisira?

0:04:04.380,0:04:09.800
Dambudziko raakatarisana naro nderokuti haana basa, hapana murume kana mubatsiri.

0:04:09.800,0:04:12.640
Kunyange kudya kuri kunetsa uye haana imba.

0:04:12.640,0:04:16.180
Saka, akasarudza kuti aizozviuraya.

0:04:16.180,0:04:18.360
Kazhinji kacho, ndaizobvuta banga kubva kwaari.

0:04:18.360,0:04:21.480
Kunyange chepfu ye kuuraya makonzo - aiti aizoinwa asi ini ndaizoitora kubva kwaari.

0:04:21.480,0:04:26.660
Matambudziko omwana wenyu - anokubatai sei, saamai?

0:04:26.660,0:04:31.360
Zvakandikanganisa. Zvekuti izvozvi, ndine dambudziko re mwoyo.

0:04:31.360,0:04:35.460
Amai ne mwana wavo - paunoteerera kwavari ...

0:04:35.460,0:04:42.500
Haugoni kuvapa mhosva nekuda kwedambudziko ravo.

0:04:42.500,0:04:48.420
Apo patinenge tichishanda, Mwari anofanira kuzviongorora.

0:04:48.420,0:05:00.120
Kureve kuti; mushure mekunge waita zvinhu zvose, zvino gonekwa ne munhu, Mwari anozofanira kuzviongorora nekuzvi maka.

0:05:00.120,0:05:01.460
Urikuona here?

0:05:01.460,0:05:10.560
Mushure mokunge wazviita zvakaperera kwauri, haugoni kuti, "Zvakanaka".

0:05:10.560,0:05:17.040
Mwari achafanira kuzviongorora bedzi ne kuzvi maka chimwe nechimwe.

0:05:17.040,0:05:20.360
Ndizvo zvatinoti nyasha.

0:05:20.380,0:05:33.120
Mushure mokunge wabudirira kana kuti wafamba unoti, "Hongu, ndinozviita zvakakwana" - semu Kristu, mutauro iwoyo hauna kunaka.

0:05:33.120,0:05:35.460
Hongu.

0:05:35.460,0:05:42.780
Seva Kristu tinorarama pasi penyasha - nyasha dzinotifukidza.

0:05:42.780,0:05:49.960
Mushure mokunge waburira kana kufamba, waita zvose zvaunogona kuita semunhu,

0:05:49.960,0:05:55.020
uye iwe unoti ichi chakanga chiri chinhu chakanaka chawakaita - zvisiye kuna Mwari.

0:05:55.020,0:05:56.740
Mwari anofanira kuitei?

0:05:56.740,0:05:59.600
Kuzvimaka.

0:05:59.600,0:06:12.320
Saka, zviri kuna Mwari kuti akupe maki, kunyangwe iri 90%, 50%, 40% kana ... zva kuna Mwari.

0:06:12.320,0:06:15.160
Ndidzo nyasha.

0:06:15.160,0:06:23.780
Kana mumwe munhu iye zvino achitaura kuti mhuri ino inofanira kupomerwa mhosva, kana kuti unovabvunza, "Iwe une maoko nemakumbo -

0:06:23.780,0:06:27.700
nei usingagoni kuenda kuno shanda? "

0:06:27.700,0:06:36.920
Zvione iwe pachezvako unofanirwa kuzvibvunza kuti isimba ripi rawakawana zvaunazvo.

0:06:36.920,0:06:39.640
Vakadzi ava - havana nzvimbo yokugara.

0:06:39.640,0:06:50.340
Kungotarisa maonekero avo ne zvipfeko - zvinodhura zvikuru uye zvakanaka -

0:06:50.340,0:06:58.120
asi izvozvo hazvigoni kupikisa Mweya wa Mwari.

0:06:58.120,0:07:05.280
Nguvo ne zvose zvaive zve kubwinya kwakare.

0:07:05.280,0:07:06.360
Chii chekare?

0:07:06.360,0:07:07.120
(Mbiri.)

0:07:07.120,0:07:11.820
Mbiri yakare - zvinhu zvavaiva nazvo munguva yakapfuura.

0:07:11.820,0:07:16.160
Saka, amai nemwanasikana ...

0:07:16.160,0:07:21.460
Taziva kuti imba yacho haisi pasi pe N200,000.

0:07:21.460,0:07:25.880
Vanofanira kuvapa N500,000 kuti vatange chimwe chinhu.

